https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/pdf/ptx_isa_7.3.pdf

Targeting NVIDIA PTX
https://developer.codeplay.com/products/computecpp/ce/guides/platform-support/targeting-nvidia-ptx?version=1.3.0

User Guide for NVPTX Back-end
https://llvm.org/docs/NVPTXUsage.html

PTX Assembly
https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/inline-ptx-assembly/index.html

NVCC - Nvidia CUDA Compiler Driver 
https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/pdf/CUDA_Compiler_Driver_NVCC.pdf


